Risk factors for metastasis and survival of patients with T1 gastric 
neuroendocrine carcinoma treated with endoscopic therapy versus surgical 
resection.

Ye H(#)(1)(2)(3), Yuan Y(#)(1)(2)(3), Chen P(1)(2)(3), Zheng Q(4)(5)(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Gastrointestinal and Hernia Ward, HwaMei Hospital, University 
of Chinese Academy of Sciences, No. 41 Xibei Street, Ningbo, Zhejiang, China.
(2)Ningbo Institute of Life and Health Industry, University of Chinese Academy 
